"Ain't It Fun" is a song by the American rock band Paramore and is the sixth track from their fourth album, self-titled Paramore. It is set to be the album's third single, but no release date has yet been confirmed.[1] Despite not yet being released as a single, the song charted at #12 on the UK Rock chart on June 8, 2013, and as of May 2013 is currently played regularly on Sydney radio station 2SSR on their Juice program.
The song received positive reviews from music critics, with some pointing it as one of the best tracks of Paramore and praising the funky/90's pop production and sarcastic lyrics.
